<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>57</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thiemgau hun gen, Immanuel,
 Tuni hin ahung pieng tai;
 Tichun Angel aw'n vabang phawng,
 Belam ching phul mun achun.

[V2]
 Van mite chun, (2)
 Thakna'n van zai a vawl ui (2)

[V3]
 2. Khawsak miching, chung van aksi,
 Singthavang lambang zawt in;
 Bethlehem dai bawng In sung ah,
 Ngulbang lupna gankuong sung.

[V4]
 Michingte chun, (2)
 A gobawmteu a hawng ui. (2)

[V5]
 3. Van Mang Theisen, Mari Vawnchawih,
 Mimbang pieng in A lieng luo'i!
 Umlo sanggah sietlei kuomluoh,
 Alieng theisen nang bang hi!

[V6]
 Lal Herod chun, (2)
 Thakiek ding thimthu a tiem. (2)

[V7]
 4. Chamna van Lengmang Herod-in,
 Pakbang in chawilo mahleh;
 Van mipi-Seraphimte chun,
 Van phaiphuleng gihawih tawh.

[V8]
 Kumsawt tawplo, (2)
 Hallelui zem kim in chawi. (2)</lyrics>
<title>THE GREAT SIGN OF IMMANUEL</title>
</song>